Future Outlook: When the Hybrid Approach Will No Longer Be Required
Once native NAP+CRG support lands (ETA CY26 per the GitHub issue and AKS roadmap), auto-provisioned pools will directly integrate with CRGs. This means:
NAP (via Karpenter) will automatically detect and prioritize reserved capacity without manual SKU constraints.
