Based on current official docs (e.g., NAP overview at https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/aks/node-auto-provisioning), this will simplify provisioning while maintaining features like dynamic SKU optimization and zonal HA.
We'll monitor Azure updates for the exact rollout (likely Q1-Q2 2026) and reassess then.
